{"tid":1284691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]希臘貼錢俾你移民過去！！！","createTime":"2019-07-04T09:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:05:34.000Z","uid":258067,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b02e748b1ac5ddb487e68a0955ff080addeffa","tid":1284691,"uid":258067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"Greek Island Will Pay You $565 A Month And Give You A Plot Of Land To Live There<br />\nAn island in Greece wants to pay people &euro;500 ($565) per month to live there. Not only that, but they will also give the new locals a plot of land to build their home or business.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nThe island of Antikythera is looking for new locals as the remote isle is home to just 24 people - which increases to 40 people during the summer.<br />\n<br />\nLocated between Crete and Kythira, it is 45 minutes by plane from Athens.<br />\n<br />\nThe scheme is sponsored by the Greek Orthodox Church, who will pay the stipend for three years.<br />\n<br />\nThey are ideally looking for young families to join the community as the population has slowly dropped from over 300 people at the beginning of the 20th century.<br />\n<br />\nYoung locals have been leaving to head to the busier Greek islands for work, resulting in an ageing population.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nThe president of the local Antikythera council, Andreas Charchalakis, told Greek website iefimerida that fishermen, stock-farmers, builders, and bakers could flourish there.<br />\n<br />\nWe are looking for many families to 'revive' our island.<br />\n<br />\nThese are professions which can guarantee a decent income for those who will come to our island.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nHowever, the island is very rustic - there is no bank or ATM on the island and there are very few shops with basic food and vegetables, which are grown on the island, along with wine.<br />\n<br />\nBut it does have electricity and internet connection.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nWhile Greek families are offered priority, the opportunity is also open to other nationalities.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to local reports, four families have already been approved for the program.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過住喺荒島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c4775d8c5fdb26a811298552da664e0b6ecfe6dd","tid":1284691,"uid":258067,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5arOwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5arOwb.jpg&h=8c68e559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/un1KAbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fun1KAbe.jpg&h=2e6430bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6a22b08e402975968ff908877e6e4962b2ad4ad","tid":1284691,"uid":120715,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"起碼間屋大過香港個D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f42764795ce5cb93c4a551ef65a39e3c4d9e0b7","tid":1284691,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"Good wor"},{"pid":"9cb5d08ed8662fcc9c85d60a1df3e2a14bbbe98e","tid":1284691,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"去完希臘返嚟成個乞衣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04bac54015a79044d879b7a1be616b9ae7a8d1f","tid":1284691,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"可以考慮"},{"pid":"e5155f157328557f67d75336d9c082dbe96ffc29","tid":1284691,"uid":70885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"住夠年數咪搬出城市囉"},{"pid":"8695e44c2da1cabee5f082aaa86b9029a48be1b9","tid":1284691,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:2