","msg":"不過真係好撚靚"},{"pid":"b34f2078721028c097dffbdbee1add74b46af794","tid":1284691,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1iEo7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1iEo7b.jpg&h=a3a23956&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1d1c894bae5f74d8d786322aacbb127d1152c3e","tid":1284691,"uid":76685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:33:13.000Z","msg":"住慣香港依啲城市方便到一個點既香港人<br />\n點可能適應到依啲地方乜都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19680988893fa7b3ce6ceb900a0e1b59b9967e4e","tid":1284691,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"二百萬人搬過去"},{"pid":"542a41ab61523ecae9168de8ce551e65b992c9e1","tid":1284691,"uid":45830,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19680988893fa7b3ce6ceb900a0e1b59b9967e4e","tid":1284691,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"二百萬人搬過去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"佢地要破多幾次產。。。。。"},{"pid":"742d051d81e2e4f4f5371c8d3cba1936846c47e2","tid":1284691,"uid":14305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"500&euro; 定 565$ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb262bea86223c2c78a1dfa7830d4bf21f5334a","tid":1284691,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"mama mia"},{"pid":"2d076f188924588bffca69a442d299d3c89d7280","tid":1284691,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"好似要識希臘文先去得"},{"pid":"adfad3e655f19be63eada28bc583dfc9406e0eca","tid":1284691,"uid":116953,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"搵左少少資料（未証實）<br />\n果個地方叫 Antikythira，係個得24個人住緊既希臘小島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umKzXLj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumKzXLj.png&h=8102489b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖中指住既就係<br />\n左邊果個小島就係 Kythira Island <br />\n<br />\n其實人地都有D要求，唔人人去都受：<br />\n1. 識希臘話/希臘人<br />\n2. 三人以上家庭<br />\n3. 成人要有小島需要既技能（捉魚，養牛羊，建築，整麵包等等）<br />\n4. 審批過程需時五年<br />\n<br />\n永久居留好處：<br />\n1. 每個家庭每月有&euro;500資助<br />\n2. 免費住宿，免費飲食<br />\n<br />\n當地交通：<br />\n坐船去最近既城市 Kythira Island 要兩個半鐘<br />\n一星期得兩日有船，而且得一來一回（同一架船，去到 Kythira 就會拆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無得即日來回）<br />\n<br />\n要去果度首先要坐 50分鐘內陸機由 雅典 去 Kythira Island<br />\n再由 Kythira Island 坐船過去<br />\n<br />\n最後貼條片比大家欣賞下當地既面貌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4x0vErBgzzE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4x0vErBgzzE&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=4135857b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4x0vErBgzzE</a><br />\n<br />\n相信香港人要移民去果度都相當唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78beed7d8924ad96808b12ddd7b70cba86e68612","tid":1284691,"uid":180975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"佢仲有錢貼我？"}]}